title: From China to Brazil, here’s how AI is regulated around the world
description: Governments around the world are scrambling to figure out how, exactly, to approach the questions posed by artificial intelligence.

title: Ukraine live briefing: Russia and Belarus disinvited from Nobel ceremony; Ukrainian billionaire detained
description: Both countries are barred from the Nobel ceremony in Sweden for a second year. Oligarch Ihor Kolomoisky is being held by Ukrainian authorities on charges including fraud.

title: War in Ukraine halted adoptions. Now some orphans are stuck in limbo.
description: Families hoping to adopt Ukrainian children face a major hurdle: Officials there have halted international adoptions until the end of the war.
